      "type": "text",
      "data": {
        "content": "<p><strong>1. Enhanced Security</strong><br>We're implementing additional security measures to better protect your account and data.</p><p><strong>2. Improved Performance</strong><br>Faster load times and smoother overall experience across all devices.</p><p><strong>3. New Dashboard</strong><br>A refreshed interface that makes it easier to find what you need.</p>",
